<h1>Subscribe to Mailing List</h1>
<p>You can subscribe to our mailing list by filling out the following form. You will be sent email requesting confirmation, to prevent others from gratuitously subscribing you. This is a private list, which means that the list of members is not available to non-members.</p>
<br />

<form method="post" class="form-horizontal" action="https://lists.discovery.wisc.edu/mailman/subscribe/swampmail" target="_blank">
	<fieldset>
		<legend>Personal info</legend>

		<div class="form-group">
			<label class="required control-label">Your email address</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<div class="input-group">
					<input type="text" class="required form-control" name="email" value="">
					<div class="input-group-addon">
						<i class="active fa fa-question-circle" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" data-container="body" title="Your email address" data-content="Please enter a valid email address.  A valid email is required for membership in the mailing list. "></i>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="form-group">
			<label class="control-label">Your name (optional)</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<div class="input-group">
					<input type="text" class="form-control" name="fullname" value="">
					<div class="input-group-addon">
						<i class="active fa fa-question-circle" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" data-container="body" title="Your name" data-content="Please enter your name. "></i>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</fieldset>


	<fieldset>
		<br />
		<legend>Password</legend>
		<p>You may enter a privacy password below. This provides only mild security, but should prevent others from messing with your subscription. <strong>Do not use a valuable password</strong> as
		it will occasionally be emailed back to you in cleartext. </p>
		<p>If you choose not to enter a password, one will be automatically generated for you, and it will be sent to you once you've confirmed your subscription.  You can always request a mail-back of your password when you edit your personal options. Once a month, your password will be emailed to you as a reminder. </p>
		<br />

		<div class="form-group">
			<label class="control-label">Password</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<div class="input-group">
					<input type="password" class="form-control" name="pw" value="">
					<div class="input-group-addon">
						<i class="active fa fa-question-circle" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" data-container="body" title="Password" data-content="Please enter your password. "></i>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="form-group">
			<label class="control-label">Reenter password to confirm</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<div class="input-group">
					<input type="password" class="form-control" name="pw-conf" value="">
					<div class="input-group-addon">
						<i class="active fa fa-question-circle" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" data-container="body" title="Reenter password" data-content="Please re-enter your password as before. "></i>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</fieldset>

	<fieldset>
		<legend>Preferences</legend>

		<div class="form-group">
			<label class="control-label">Would you like to receive list mail batched in a daily digest?</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<input type=radio name="digest" value="0" CHECKED> No
				<input type=radio name="digest" value="1"> Yes
			</div>
		</div>
	</fieldset>

	<div class="bottom buttons">
		<button type="submit" name="email-button" value="Subscribe" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i>Submit</button>
	</div>

</form>
